item.title: Con nhớ cha (I miss you daddy)
item.description: I miss you daddy Tác giả: Julia Michaels (Mỹ) It’s been a year daddy I really really miss you Mommy says you’re safe now In a beautiful place called heaven We had your favorite dinner tonight And I ate it all up… Even though I don’t like carrots I learned how to swim this summer And I can even open my eyes When I’m under water Can you see me?
